Package org.opensourcephysics.resources.media

Class video

java.lang.Object
java.util.ResourceBundle
java.util.PropertyResourceBundle
org.opensourcephysics.resources.media.video
Direct Known Subclasses:
video_en, video_es, video_zh
public class video extends PropertyResourceBundle
Resource loader for OSP video package. Resource strings are obtained from properties. Defining a Java resource class speeds up resource loading, particularly for applets because a connection to the server is not required.
Author:
Wolfgang Christian
